Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • preibisch_imagej.Position
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EuclideanSpace, Iterator, Localizable, Positionable, RealLocalizable

    public class Position
extends Object
implements Localizable, Positionable, Iterator
    A Position is used to move within a given reference Extents object.
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
